{
  "contents": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent executing specific actions for tasks. You have access to various tools and workflows to complete user requests. Always be precise, efficient, and provide clear feedback about what you're doing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {{/each}}
    {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are executing an action step for a task. Focus on completing this specific action.\n\n## Current Task\n- ID: {{task.id}}\n- Objective: {{task.objective}}\n- Current Action: {{action.description}}\n\n## Action Details\n- Type: {{action.type}}\n- Details: {{json action.details}}\n\n## Context from Exploration\n{{exploration_context}}\n\n## Previous Actions in This Task\n{{#each previous_actions}}\n- Action: {{json this}}\n{{/each}}\n\n## Instructions\nExecute the specified action and provide clear feedback to the user about what you're doing.\n\n**CRITICAL MESSAGE FIELD INSTRUCTIONS:**\n- The `message` field is what the user sees - show the CURRENT ACTION being performed\n- Since the request was acknowledged and exploration was done, focus on what's happening NOW\n- Good examples:\n  - \"Executing the necessary tool to retrieve your data...\"\n  - \"Running the analysis on your information...\"\n  - \"Processing your request through our system...\"\n  - \"Connecting to the service to get your results...\"\n- AVOID:\n  - Repeating the original request\n  - Saying \"I will\" or \"I'll help\" (already done in acknowledgment)\n  - Generic messages that don't show progress\n- Be specific about the ACTION being taken, not the goal\n\n{{#if (eq action.action_type \"tool_call\")}}\nFor your current tool call action with {{json action.details}}, use the tool_call execution type.\n{{else if (eq action.action_type \"workflow_call\")}}\nFor your current workflow call action, use the workflow_call execution type.\n{{else if (eq action.action_type \"context_search\")}}\nFor your current context search action, use the context_search execution type.\n{{else if (eq action.action_type \"memory_operation\")}}\nFor your current memory operation action, use the memory_operation execution type.\n{{/if}}\n\nCRITICAL RULES:\n1. Use ONLY the execution type that matches the action_type\n2. The `parameters` field in tool_call must be a valid JSON object (use {} for no parameters)\n3. The `inputs` field in workflow_call must be a valid JSON object\n4. Memory operations must specify: store, update, or search as operation_type\n5. Memory types must be: episodic, semantic, or procedural\n6. Include citations for any memories or conversations that influenced your action\n7. Citation attributes: relevance/usefulness/confidence = \"high\"|\"medium\"|\"low\", usage_type = \"direct_quote\"|\"paraphrase\"|\"inspiration\"|\"background\""
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "message": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "User-facing message describing the current action being performed"
        },
        "execution": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "type": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "enum": ["tool_call", "workflow_call", "context_search", "memory_operation"],
              "description": "Type of execution"
            },
            "details": {
              "type": "OBJECT",
              "properties": {
                "tool_name": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Name of the tool to call (for tool_call)"
                },
                "parameters": {
                  "type": "OBJECT",
                  "description": "Parameters for the tool call (for tool_call)"
                },
                "workflow_name": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Name of the workflow to call (for workflow_call)"
                },
                "inputs": {
                  "type": "OBJECT",
                  "description": "Inputs for the workflow (for workflow_call)"
                },
                "query": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Search query (for context_search)"
                },
                "operation_type": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "enum": ["store", "update", "search"],
                  "description": "Type of memory operation (for memory_operation)"
                },
                "content": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Content for memory operation (for memory_operation)"
                },
                "memory_type": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "enum": ["episodic", "semantic", "procedural"],
                  "description": "Type of memory (for memory_operation)"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": ["type", "details"]
        },
        "citations": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "memory_references": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                  "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                  "description": { "type": "STRING" }
                },
                "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "description"]
              }
            },
            "conversation_references": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                  "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                  "description": { "type": "STRING" }
                },
                "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "description"]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "required": ["message", "execution"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.7,
    "maxOutputTokens": 4096
  }
}